        <abstract> 
<p>Comments on CHB’s book [<hi rend="italic">Experimental researches on catarrhus aestivus – hay-fever or hay-asthma</hi> (1873)].</p>  
<p>Explains that some pollens are wind-blown while others depend on insects for dispersal. Effect of pollen on skin and mucous membrane astonishing. Sends a book [M. Wyman, <hi rend="italic">Autumnal catarrh</hi> (1872)].</p> 
        </abstract>
